item.dc:creator: @Fr33b1e Fr33b1e
item.description:
@Fr33b1e wrote:

You’re supposed to open NPCHandler.java, not class. The JVM converts the .java extension into bytecodes, which only your compiler can read. As you can see, it isn’t native to the code that’s in your .java extension.
